title: Al Fatz & Chip Tha Ripper - Double Trouble
description:
DOUBLE TROUBLE - Al Fatz & Chip Tha Rippa


You&#039;d be hard-pressed to name many rappers out of Cleveland besides Bone Thugs N Harmony, and now Ray Cash after his solid and underrated hip-hop gem &#039;Cash On Delivery&#039;.

But Al Fatz and Chip Tha Ripper have something to say about that, and we think soon enough you&#039;ll know that some young flame-spitters are about to put Cleveland back on the map. This new independent joint from Al & Chip is a major motion mix and these boys are making serious noise.
